    <h1>Content Security Policy</h1>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-9">
            <p>
                Content Security Policy is a web standard widely supported in modern browsers that offers an additional layer of
                protection against cross-site scripting attacks.  CSP can help prevent XSS exploitation when you've failed to
                escape untrusted output properly or consider every vector for code injection.
            </p>
        </div>
